d 'SEARCHFOR': Universal search utility — find any text, number, or pattern across Stata variables
d
d  searchfor searches every variable in the active dataset (or a
d  user-specified subset) and reports: which variables contain the
d  search term, hit counts, percentage of matching observations, and
d  the exact observation (row) numbers where matches occur.
d
d  The command handles string variables (partial or exact match,
d  case-insensitive by default) and numeric variables (exact equality,
d  or value-label search via the vallabel option).  All results are
d  stored in r() for programmatic use.
d
d KW: search
d KW: data exploration
d KW: find
d KW: text search
d KW: pattern matching
d KW: variable contents
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260421
d
d Author: Your Name, Your Institution
d Support: email you@email.com
d
f searchfor.ado
f searchfor.sthlp
